title: ArtyTorrent Pack 53-Electro Breaks Drum Loops 120-129 bpm-WAV
description:
ArtyTorrent Pack 53-Electro Breaks Drum Loops 120-129 bpm-WAV
-------------------------------------------------------------

Quite a large pack of electro loops here. These are at house tempo, but have more of an old skool syncopated feel. They could be used in several genres of electronic music. This pack should keep electroheads busy for a while, but a separate Electro House pack (containing four to the floor beats) will follow later.
The tempo of these samples ranges from 120-129 bpm.

Torrent contains 6 RAR files with 345 loops
-------------------------------------------
Chicago Fire Electro 120-129 (22 loops)
Ghetto Electro Breaks 120-129 (97 loops)
Machine Language Electro 120-129 (20 loops)
Magix Electro Drums 120 (166 loops)
Misc Electro Breaks 120-129 (36 loops)
VEE Electro Loops 128 (4 loops)

All samples have been normalized and acidized and are 16-bit WAVs at 44.1KHz, looped precisely and containing the approx bpm in the filenames.

The samples are from a variety of sources including CDs produced by Sonic Foundry/Sony, Magix, EastWest, Tekniks and Vengeance.

--
Arty - "Electrocution"
13th February 2008.
